  * Fix: q3n help brief listing missing fortune/validate/cite/run/config
  * Fix: q3n tutorial missing wikipedia:// and github:// from scheme list
  * Fix: man page — added --version to SYNOPSIS; removed dangling q3n(7) reference
  * Fix: q3n.appdata.xml scheme count (16 schemes, listed http)
  * Fix: spec/man page now documents youtube:// as yt:// alias
  * Chore: migrated CI from GitHub Actions to Woodpecker (.woodpecker/*.yml)
  * Chore: removed .github/ directory
